languages.text: "Неизвестность разбивает мне сердце, шерин, но я уважаю ваш выбор. Я бы тоже подумала дважды, а затем еще раз, прежде чем отправлять своих ребят одному Великому известно за чем".

languages.text: "The not knowing is tearing me apart, shereen, but I do respect your decision. I would think twice — and think again — in your shoes before I sent my own guys off to only the Exalted One knows where."

languages.text: “无法得知真相的感觉几乎要让我崩溃，亲爱的，但我尊重你的决定。换做是我，若是要把我的人送到只有至高无上的神皇才知道的地方之前，我会三思，再三思。”
languages.original_text: "The not knowing is tearing me apart, shereen, but I do respect your decision. I would think twice — and think again — in your shoes before I sent my own guys off to only the Exalted One knows where."

languages.text: «Me está matando esto de no saber, shereen, pero respeto la decisión. En su lugar también me lo pensaría dos veces... y hasta tres... antes de enviar a mis muchachos a un lugar desconocido».
languages.original_text: "The not knowing is tearing me apart, shereen, but I do respect your decision. I would think twice — and think again — in your shoes before I sent my own guys off to only the Exalted One knows where."

languages.text: 「知らないなんて胸が引き裂かれるよ、シャリーン、でもその決断力をほんとに尊敬ものだよ。あたしがアンタの立場なら、エグザルテッド・ワンのみぞ知る場所に部下を送り出す前にじっくり考えて…考えに考えちゃうね…」
languages.original_text: "The not knowing is tearing me apart, shereen, but I do respect your decision. I would think twice — and think again — in your shoes before I sent my own guys off to only the Exalted One knows where."

traits.locale_text: 「知らないなんて胸が引き裂かれるよ、シャリーン、でもその決断力をほんとに尊敬ものだよ。あたしがアンタの立場なら、エグザルテッド・ワンのみぞ知る場所に部下を送り出す前にじっくり考えて…考えに考えちゃうね…」
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: « J'ai du mal à supporter de ne pas savoir, shereen, mais je respecte votre décision. Moi aussi, j'y réfléchirais à deux fois, si ce n'est trois, avant d'envoyer mes hommes je ne sais où. »
languages.original_text: "The not knowing is tearing me apart, shereen, but I do respect your decision. I would think twice — and think again — in your shoes before I sent my own guys off to only the Exalted One knows where."

traits.locale_text: « J'ai du mal à supporter de ne pas savoir, shereen, mais je respecte votre décision. Moi aussi, j'y réfléchirais à deux fois, si ce n'est trois, avant d'envoyer mes hommes je ne sais où. »
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: "Nicht Bescheid zu wissen, zerreißt mich förmlich, Shereen, aber ich respektiere Eure Entscheidung. Auch ich würde mir an Eurer Stelle zweimal überlegen – und dann noch ein drittes Mal –, ob ich meine eigenen Leute an einen Ort schicke, von dem nur der Erhabene weiß, was sie dort erwartet."

languages.text: "Şirinim, ne olduğunu öğrenemezsem içim içimi yiyecek ama kararına saygı duyuyorum. Yerinde olsam teferruatını ancak Görkemli'nin bileceği bir yere adamlarımı göndermeden evvel iki kez düşünür, üstüne bir daha düşünürdüm."
languages.original_text: "The not knowing is tearing me apart, shereen, but I do respect your decision. I would think twice — and think again — in your shoes before I sent my own guys off to only the Exalted One knows where."
